/ End demo 
.demo-description
  %p   
    Another great feature in 3.6 version is suppor of Right To Left languages.
    This is done just with the option 
    %i
      direction
    in jqGrid options.
  %p
    Note that in a page one grid can have the direction set to rtl, while another can have direction
    set to ltr. Support of RTL is provided only in FireFox 3.x, Internet Explorer 7/8 and partially
    in Opera > 9.x browsers.
  %p
    To fully enjoy this feature we have created a demo page with all the examples
    = link_to "here", "http://www.trirand.com/blog/jqgrid/jqgrid.html"
    \.   
/ End demo-description
